qoutes.text: Life with you has been an incredible journey, and I know in my heart that I want to keep walking this path with you, through all the highs and lows, the joys and challenges.
I cannot imagine a future that doesn't include your laughter, your kindness, and your unwavering support
Every moment with you has been a beautiful journey, and with every step, my heart has found its true home in you
I want to continue this adventure with you by my side

propose.text: Life is unpredictable, full of twists and turns, and while I may not know what the future holds, there is one thing I am absolutely certain of: my love for you. It’s a love that has grown stronger with each passing day, and it’s a love that I want to cherish for the rest of my life.
